title: ePSXe 1.9
description:
This has a Playstation Emulator + Gameboy Emulator with a good collection of games and everything is pretty much set up for ePSXe 1.9, i got all the plugins that you will need, also if your gunna be playing any of the final fantasy games if you look at the "readme" i have a good video set-up for ff7 through ff9 plus instructions to set up everything, so i hope it works for you guys like it did for me, also i want to make a note that i didn't try out all of the games yet but all of the ones that i set-up they all worked so enjoy and good luck!

P.S. If you have any questions please feel free to ask and i will try to help you the best i can!
